{"tid":1725854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防暴警聲言拘捕商台記者　向其背部發海綿彈","createTime":"2019-11-16T01:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T02:23:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"796f3ba7776fc1528551a81b0ade4b0fa3423d21","tid":1725854,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:58:51.000Z","msg":"警方凌晨於旺角清場期間，有警員向一名記者發射懷疑海綿彈。<br />\n<br />\n網上片段顯示，警方於亞皆老街驅散時，推撞一名《商業電台》記者，該名記者背向防暴警員後退，期間一名防暴警員隨即向該名記者背部開防暴槍，發射懷疑海綿彈。<br />\n<br />\n據《商業電台》報道，警員當時指該名記者涉嫌暴動，記者讀出警員行動呼號及準備拍攝，警員聲稱要拘捕記者，記者背囊有破洞，現場發現一個海綿彈彈頭，記者未有受傷。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492534-20191116.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492534-20191116.htm&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BEngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=a17f0fe9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492534-20191116.htm&h=033cb667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492534-20191116.htm</a>"},{"pid":"185553c9f506bf8bc4791f2cd8d254fced6b6eae","tid":1725854,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:23:13.000Z","msg":"涉嫌暴動<br />\n暴佢老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}